{"tid":1724247,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視風向問題]凌晨12點後出post加[(N)ight標籤","createTime":"2019-11-15T12:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T16:04:28.000Z","uid":28252,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"02adaff7d571538afb99ed4574014131ff704a16","tid":1724247,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"一直以黎連登都有凌晨問題，大量三毛post會係凌晨時份突然轉風向，令到連登仔每朝早都要忍受三毛post嘅摧殘，嚴重影響討論區氣氛以及對連登平台不利。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想Admin考慮以下建議：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會員係凌晨十二點至六點出嘅post，加返個N字，並維持掛上直至當日完結。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">加係P字嘅右邊</span><br />\n<br />\n等一眾連登仔可以增加對外來勢力嘅警介，從而<span style=\"color: red;\">降低凌晨時份轉風向嘅勢力</span>，如果加N字可以令到風向撚要係非凌晨嘅時間出post，甚至會<span style=\"color: red;\">減弱凌晨時份嘅風力</span>，因為如果面對清醒嘅連登仔，久而久之佢應該係會唔夠訓嘅。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n香港人 Assemble!<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccfb0eecd7e52069410d81df0628bbeaf43be36","tid":1724247,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"挑機風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e45378aa94266307f1e833f02df9ef035a9cba","tid":1724247,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"挑機呀風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc163277e1f0a53b2323e114c58afa2f6143519","tid":1724247,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"挑機呀風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c380a4a5d807dc5aa551b819a24aca2f2ea8c0c9","tid":1724247,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"挑機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739e9d4a04bb0786252383afb0ca99b1cecf77ca","tid":1724247,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-